1. Ovaj grad je *postalo* mesto gde se ljudi često okupljaju. (This city has become a place where people often gather).

2. On je *postalo* pravi majstor u svojim rukama. (He has become a real master in his hands).

3. *Postalo* je jasno da su potrebne promene. (It has become clear that changes are needed).

4. *Postalo* je još toplije nego što je bilo. (It has become even warmer than it was).

5. On je *postalo* očigledno nervozan. (He has become obviously nervous).